<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>There are two kinds of show events: show events caused by the window system (spontaneous), and internal show events. Spontaneous (<db:link xlink:href="qevent.xml#spontaneous">QEvent::spontaneous</db:link>()) show events are sent just after the window system shows the window; they are also sent when a top-level window is redisplayed after being iconified. Internal show events are delivered just before the widget becomes visible.</db:para>
